window.bookSummaryJSON = "It is now six years since the secret disaster at Jurassic Park, six years since the extraordinary dream of science and imagination came to a crashing end - the dinosaurs destroyed, the park dismantled, the island indefinitely closed to the public. <p>But there are rumors that something has survived.</p>"; 
